query:
SELECT id, siteId, status, DATE_FORMAT(startDate, '%Y-%m-%d') as start_dt, DATE_FORMAT(endDate, '%Y-%m-%d') as end_dt, ownerAmount 
FROM bookings 
WHERE status = 'confirmed' 
AND startDate >= '2026-01-01' AND startDate < '2026-02-01';
